trans-unit.source: Implements the basic functionality for a collection of table layout styles.
trans-unit.target: Implementerar grundläggande funktioner för en samling av layout tabellformat.

trans-unit.source: The TableLayoutStyleCollection class represents the collection of all the styles used to describe the columns or rows in an associated <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel>.
trans-unit.target: Klassen TableLayoutStyleCollection representerar samling med alla format som används för att beskriva kolumner eller rader i en associerad <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel>

trans-unit.source: Classes derived from TableLayoutStyleCollection are specialized as follows: - A <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutColumnStyleCollection> aggregates column styles as a collection of <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ColumnStyle> objects.
trans-unit.target: Klasser som härleds från TableLayoutStyleCollection är specialiserade på följande sätt: - A <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutColumnStyleCollection>aggregerar kolumnformat som en samling <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ColumnStyle>objekt.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ColumnStyle> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutColumnStyleCollection>

trans-unit.source: - A <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutRowStyleCollection> aggregates row styles as a collection of <xref:System.Windows.Forms.RowStyle> objects.
trans-unit.target: -A <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutRowStyleCollection>mängder rad formatmallar som en samling <xref:System.Windows.Forms.RowStyle>objekt.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.RowStyle> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutRowStyleCollection>

trans-unit.source: Most of the members of TableLayoutStyleCollection are implementations of <xref:System.Collections.IList>.
trans-unit.target: De flesta av medlemmarna i TableLayoutStyleCollection är implementeringar av <xref:System.Collections.IList>.</xref:System.Collections.IList>

trans-unit.source: The Add method reapplies the table layout to all the controls in the current <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel> container.

trans-unit.source: The Clear method performs two main actions: - It disassociates the current <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutStyleCollection> from its <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel> container so that the styles are no longer applied to the layout of the controls contained within the panel.
trans-unit.target: Metoden Clear utför två huvudsakliga åtgärder:-det tas aktuellt <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutStyleCollection>från dess <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel>behållare så att formatmallarna som inte längre tillämpas på layout för de kontroller som finns i panelen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutStyleCollection>

trans-unit.source: As a result, the table layout is reapplied to all the controls in the panel.
trans-unit.target: Därför används layouten Tabell igen till alla kontroller i panelen.

trans-unit.source: - It empties the collection of all of its <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutStyle> objects.
trans-unit.target: – Det tömmer insamling av alla dess <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutStyle>objekt.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutStyle>

trans-unit.source: As a result, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutStyleCollection.Count%2A> property is set to 0.
trans-unit.target: Därför kan den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutStyleCollection.Count%2A>egenskap är inställd på 0.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutStyleCollection.Count%2A>
